articles.title: Fire erupts on cargo ship at the Port of Los Angeles, triggering major emergency at North America’s busiest port - CNN
articles.description: A fire that erupted Friday evening on a cargo ship docked at the Port of Los Angeles — requiring more than 180 firefighters to battle the blaze — is now “substantially contained,” according to a news release Saturday from the seaport.
